    • Constructor Detail

      • TwofishParameters

        public TwofishParameters()
        Initializes the TwofishParameters. The default transformation is 'Twofish/CBC/PKCS5Padding' with a block size of 16 bytes and key size of 128 bits.

      • TwofishParameters

        public TwofishParameters(TextEncoder textEncoder)
        Initializes the TwofishParameters with a TextEncoder which is used to decode the key when set as a string. The default transformation is 'Twofish/CBC/PKCS5Padding' with a block size of 16 bytes and key size of 128 bits.
        Parameters:
        textEncoder - the TextEncoder
